  "answer": "Divorce types include revocable (raj'i) and irrevocable (ba'in). The text details conditions such as the necessity of intention (niyyah), the effect of pronouncements, the role of witnesses, and the impact of factors like menstruation and waiting periods ('iddah'). It also discusses the effects of divorce on marital rights and obligations.",
